{"tid":382253,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"另一半相似好定互補好","createTime":"2017-08-31T14:22:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T16:55:50.000Z","uid":101178,"like":8,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8448d9f9d3c8c8cb6a96e189a7534644f0298000","tid":382253,"uid":101178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T14:22:44.000Z","msg":"有時諗如果呢個世界有另一個我<br />\n同佢相處一定會好累 因為睇對方一個眼神一個動作就知佢想點 有冇呃自己<br />\n<br />\n咁如果另一半係一個同自己好似嘅人<br />\n係咪都會咁悶咁累 定係會相處得好舒服<br />\n好多嘢都唔使講<br />\n<br />\n定還是大家都唔似 可以互補不足<br />\n佢可以用另一個角度幫你諗 一正一負一凹一凸<br />\n但磨擦又會多好多<br />\n<br />\n大家想你嘅伴侶同自己相似好定可以互補好？<br />\n<br />\n正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：相似<br />\n負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：互補"},{"pid":"d2fe1bc1816a384fd4ebc0725d993d182879f591","tid":382253,"uid":20736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T14:29:28.000Z","msg":"梗係相似好 有共同興趣好玩好多"},{"pid":"cad4127bcb620ef9874d0a1e3c2fd28f23488349","tid":382253,"uid":101178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T14:35:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>梗係相似好 有共同興趣好玩好多</blockquote><br />\n唔會累咩 大家諗咩都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd04a2fdbe1adf1702e0c1c9d5b1c0ac826ba7f","tid":382253,"uid":101178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T14:48:56.000Z","msg":"點解咁多人覺得互補好啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"789af224e1f36002aecec902d8adb923efd13cd0","tid":382253,"uid":34051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T15:03:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>梗係相似好 有共同興趣好玩好多</blockquote><br />\n唔會累咩 大家諗咩都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即使唔相似 總有一日都會了解曬大家有興趣了解對方既野<br />\n冇共同話題就好易dead air"},{"pid":"76ab17254bdfe4e6694c3670c06f657e6a4c2122","tid":382253,"uid":115159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T15:04:16.000Z","msg":"樓主點解覺得相似會好攰？<br />\n對方一個小動作，你已經知佢下一步<br />\n或者 對方講完一句說話，你再講埋佢下一句<br />\n呢種心有靈犀 其實幾窩心甜蜜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ec31e8891d08530b070d05c7bcee7859cac8710","tid":382253,"uid":103049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T15:06:15.000Z","msg":"明明本來兩個人都唔似, 但愈相處就愈黎愈似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e652dbb99bf64be57bca7b6dfc61852f64608454","tid":382253,"uid":101178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T15:16:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>梗係相似好 有共同興趣好玩好多</blockquote><br />\n唔會累咩 大家諗咩都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即使唔相似 總有一日都會了解曬大家有興趣了解對方既野<br />\n冇共同話題就好易dead air</blockquote><br />\n但我覺得反而唔相似有更多話題<br />\n因為大家鐘意同所知嘅嘢唔同 可以各自分享俾對方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f245a804c0d0fdb28df35df1e70b4bdffeeb75","tid":382253,"uid":101178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T15:16:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主點解覺得相似會好攰？<br />\n對方一個小動作，你已經知佢下一步<br />\n或者 對方講完一句說話，你再講埋佢下一句<br />\n呢種心有靈犀 其實幾窩心甜蜜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為有時候唔係所有嘢都想佢知道同估到<br />\n會想有自己少少空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e930491b1f82671e8868f492bb079dd159b4c78","tid":382253,"uid":101178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T15:17:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明明本來兩個人都唔似, 但愈相處就愈黎愈似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但要雙方都磨合好先會似 如果唔係就會分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26877764b299e8791bdacfbcf46e05fc7bffe3b2","tid":382253,"uid":34051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T16:55:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>梗係相似好 有共同興趣好玩好多</blockquote><br />\n唔會累咩 大家諗咩都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即使唔相似 總有一日都會了解曬大家有興趣了解對方既野<br />\n冇共同話題就好易dead air</blockquote><br />\n但我覺得反而唔相似有更多話題<br />\n因為大家鐘意同所知嘅嘢唔同 可以各自分享俾對方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以就係話 總有一日可以知既野知曬<br />\n冇咗當初吸引大家既所謂新鮮感<br />\n咁下場就會慘過相似既情侶"}]}